Sherston America is the US office for Sherston Publishing Group (more commonly known as Sherston Software), the British software publisher. The American office supplies UK published CD-ROMs and online content and also resources developed specifically for the North American market. Sherston America was founded in 2009 and has its principal office in Portland, Oregon. 
